OL,3,CThe boy inspiring pioneering hospital
OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Merseyside
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Andy Bonner watched
OL,8,FArchie visit the new facility for the
OL,9,Ffirst time.
OL,11,FA 10-year-old boy is inspiring a
OL,12,Fcampaign to introduce new hospital
OL,13,Ffacilities across the country to help
OL,14,Fput adults with additional needs at
OL,15,Fease before going into surgery.
OL,17,FArchie Hardman was diagnosed with
OL,18,Fautism when he was three.
