OL,3,CThe boy inspiring pioneering hospital
OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FHis mum Becky Brumpton, who is a
OL,7,Fnurse, realised that while there are
OL,8,Fcalming sensory rooms available for
OL,9,Fyoung people with special needs there
OL,10,Fis a growing demand to specifically
OL,11,Fhelp adults.
OL,13,FShe is spearheading a campaign to see
OL,14,Fthe rooms introduced in hospitals
OL,15,Fnationally and hopes it will encourage
OL,16,Fmore people to access the health
OL,17,Fservices they need.
