OL,3,CThe boy inspiring pioneering hospital
OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FBecky said: "I thought my Archie is
OL,7,Fgoing to be 16 one day, so let's
OL,8,Fchange his future as well as changing
OL,9,Fpeople's futures."
OL,11,FBecky ran the London Marathon as part
OL,12,Fof the efforts to raise money for a
OL,13,Fsensory room at Arrowe Park Hospital,
OL,14,FWirral, where she is a deputy sister
OL,15,Fin the surgical elective admissions
OL,16,Flounge.
OL,18,FThe facility - the first in the
OL,19,Fcountry for adults with additional
OL,20,Fneeds attending pre-surgery - opened
OL,21,Fin 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
