OL,3,CThe boy inspiring pioneering hospital
OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FThe rooms at the Royal feature colour-
OL,7,Fchanging wall panels, plinths with
OL,8,Ffibre optic lights, wall projectors
OL,9,Fand interactive sound panels and
OL,10,Fspecial soft furnishings.
OL,12,FThe suites offer a relaxed environment
OL,13,Fspecifically for adult patients with
OL,14,Fthe likes of autism and attention
OL,15,Fdeficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)
OL,16,Fwho are having planned surgery.
OL,18,FThe facilities can also save the NHS
OL,19,Fmoney, by reducing the need for strong
OL,20,Fsedatives and further care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
