OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FBecky said: "This cohort of patients
OL,7,Funfortunately suffer from barriers to
OL,8,Faccessing health care, health care
OL,9,Finequalities due to the fact that they
OL,10,Fsimply can't attend hospital as (it
OL,11,Fis) too clinical.
OL,13,F"So by putting the sensory equipment
OL,14,Finto hospitals, we're facilitating
OL,15,Fthem being able to actually come in,
OL,16,Freceive their treatment and live
OL,17,Fhealthy, long, happy lives."
