OL,3,CThe boy inspiring pioneering hospital
OL,4,Ccare for adults with additional needs
OL,6,FSue Ryan, Divisional Nurse Director
OL,7,Ffor Surgery at the Royal, which is
OL,8,Fpart of LiverpoolJUniversity Hospitals
OL,9,FNHS Foundation Trust (LUHFT), had
OL,10,Fpreviously worked alongsideJBecky at
OL,11,FArrowe Park.
OL,13,FShe secured funding from the
OL,14,Fhospital's charity for the suites,
OL,15,Fwhile volunteers from the trust's
OL,16,Festates and facilities team fitted the
OL,17,Frooms.
OL,19,FSue said, "We were delighted to be
OL,20,Fable to work alongside Becky to make
OL,21,Fher vision aJreality at the Royal.
