OL,6,F"The rooms are a fantastic addition to
OL,7,Fthe Royal. Our goal is to role
OL,8,FArchie's Place out across our LUHFT
OL,9,Fsites to ensure that our surgical
OL,10,Fpatients with additional needs receive
OL,11,Fthe highest quality care when they
OL,12,Fattend our hospitals."
OL,14,FDavid Melia, Chief Nursing Officer at
OL,15,FLiverpool University Hospitals added:
OL,16,F"It is going to have a positive impact
OL,17,Ffor our patients.
